<p><b>Which tool is being used at step 2 of Womack & Jones?</b> Step 2: Map the Value Stream You can use a tool such as Value Stream Mapping (VSM) to do this. VSM emphasizes those parts of the process that add value, and highlights the areas where waste occurs and can be eliminated.</p>
